                   <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4"><tr bgcolor="#000000"><td><font color="#FFFFFF"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial" size="6">Max of Tat - BHBM</font></td></tr></table><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Author</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Max of Tat</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Description</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">A very versital Bring Him Before Me deck with a good balance between of Ground and Space, Dueling and non-dueling. And a nice tournament record over the last 3 months. (Only 1 loss! And that was Timed.) (=</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Bring Him Before Me<br>
